This is a 30 minute workout called 'Day 28 - 30 MIN Stretch, Relax & Recover Workout - Mobility, No Equipment, No Repeat' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
